title: Minutemen Scans Week of 06.18.08 (complete edition)
description:
Another week comes to an end. and loads of new and old books appear this week. As excited as I was to see Incredible Hercules 118, Iron Man 30, & Path of the Assassin 10 I have to say whether you like Wolverine or not, the last five issues have been awesome. Mark Millar's first story in Wolverine 66 rocks.

I have to be honest though, next Wednesday's books have me drooling. Seriously. Just look:

Captain America #39
Fantastic Four #558
Green Lantern #32
Mighty Avengers #15
New Avengers #42
Ultimates 3 #4
Thunderbolts #121
Uncanny X-Men #499
X-Men: Legacy #213


See ya Thursday night.
